{"id":481652,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_the_Humanities","text":"The University of the Humanities is a public university in Ulaanbaatar, Mongolia. The Mongolian name is \u0425\u04AF\u043C\u04AF\u04AF\u043D\u043B\u044D\u0433\u0438\u0439\u043D \u0443\u0445\u0430\u0430\u043D\u044B \u0438\u0445 \u0441\u0443\u0440\u0433\u0443\u0443\u043B\u044C. It has undergraduate and graduate programs. Fields of study include foreign languages, translation, education, journalism, computer science, economics and business.\nThe school is in downtown Ulaanbaatar at Grand Chinggis Khaan Square. The university is accredited by the Mongolian National Council for Education Accreditation.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"University","surface_form":"university","offset":45},{"uri":"Ulaanbaatar","surface_form":"Ulaanbaatar","offset":59},{"uri":"Mongolia","surface_form":"Mongolia","offset":72},{"uri":"Undergraduate_education","surface_form":"undergraduate","offset":144},{"uri":"Graduate_school","surface_form":"graduate","offset":162},{"uri":"Language","surface_form":"foreign languages","offset":205},{"uri":"Translation","surface_form":"translation","offset":224},{"uri":"Education","surface_form":"education","offset":237},{"uri":"Journalism","surface_form":"journalism","offset":248},{"uri":"Computer_science","surface_form":"computer science","offset":260},{"uri":"Economics","surface_form":"economics","offset":278},{"uri":"Business","surface_form":"business","offset":292},{"uri":"Downtown","surface_form":"downtown","offset":319},{"uri":"Accreditation","surface_form":"accredited","offset":390}]}